2. Uththhaanam cheythudane thanne kurishicha
Sehiyone nashippichu, sabhaa paanigrahanatthe
Otthuyirin than meshayorukkam cheythathinull
Than rakthamathil chertthorapputhrannaayu sthothram;
/tsthothram sleebaayaal veendavanaay;
/tsthothram chaavaaluyir chertthavanaay;
Sthothram punyatthinu thanu rudhirangall thannavanaay.
